# Git

- **Commits**: Conventional Commits — `feat:` `fix:` `chore:` `docs:` `refactor:` `test:` `ci:` (optional scope: `chore(web): …`)
- **Messages**: imperative mood, one logical change per commit; body only when context needed
- **Branches**: `main` protected; feature `feat/short-topic`, fix `fix/issue-123-short`
- **Pre-commit**: no `node_modules`, build dirs, `.env*`, logs, `.cursor/cache/`
- **PRs**: small diffs; link issue; note Web/API/DB impact when relevant
